LoggedAction
Direct Known Subclasses:
AtomicChangeConceptAction
public class AtomicChangeConceptAction
extends AtomicAction

Represents an action to change the atom that an ConceptElement is connected to. Typically this moves an Atom, Attribute, or Relationship from one Concept to another.

Author:
MEME Group
